mn dI murId lukweI mwieAw dy ipAwr dy kwrn (shI jIvn-rwh qoN) KuMJI hoeI bhuq ivlkdI iPrdI hY ]3]
(ieh isRStI pYdw kr ky pRBU ny Awp hI) ies dy ivc hI haumY qy mwieAw pYdw kr id`qI hY[
mn dy ip`Cy qurn vwlI lukweI ny (haumY mwieAw dy kwrn) kurwhy pY ky AwpxI ie`zq gvw leI hY[
ijhVw mnu`K gurU dy snmuK rihMdw hY, auh prmwqmw dy nwm ivc msq rihMdw hY (qy nwm dI brkiq nwl auh) sdw-iQr rihx vwly prmwqmw ivc lIn rihMdw hY ]4]
