aus dy AMdr prmwqmw dw ipAwr bixAw rihMdw hY, auh mnu`K prmwqmw dI BgqI ivc rMigAw rihMdw hY[ Awqmk Afolqw vwlI bu`DI dy kwrn pRBU nwl aus dI pRqIq bxI rihMdI hY ]6]
gurU dI rwhIN ijs mnu`K ny du`KW dy nws krn vwly pRBU nwl fUMGI sWJ pw leI,
sB dwqW dyx vwlw qy jgq dw Awsrw pRBU Awp aus nUM Aw imilAw[
auhI mnu`K Awqmk jIvn dI sUJ pRwpq krdw hY, ijs nUM pRBU Awp BgqI ivc joVdw hY[ aus mnu`K dy AMdroN hryk iksm dw fr hryk Brm dUr ho jWdw hY ]7]
ijs mnu`K nUM pRBU Awp hI gurU dy snmuK r`Kdw hY ijs nUM Awp hI BgqI dI dwq dyNdw hY, auh mnu`K gurU dI srn ipAw rihMdw hY[
auh mnu`K sdw-iQr pRBU dI is&q-swlwh dy Sbd ivc juiVAw rihMdw hY[
sdw-iQr rihx vwly prmwqmw nwl aus dI AijhI pRIq bx jWdI hY ik aus pRIq nUM nwh buFypw qy nwh hI Awqmk mOq q`k skdy hn (Bwv, nwh auh pRIq kdy kmzor huMdI hY qy nwh hI auQy ivkwrW nUM Awaux dw mOkw imldw hY) ]8]
jgq mwieAw dI iqRSnw dI A`g ivc sV irhw hY,
ivkwrW ivc sV sV ky bhuq du`KI ho irhw hY[
Awpxy mn dy ip`Cy qurn vwlw mnu`K (ies A`g qoN bcwau dw) QW kdy BI nhIN l`B skdw[ (auhI mnu`K bcwau dw QW l`Bdw hY ijs nUM) gurU Awqmk jIvn dI sUJ b^Sdw hY ]9]
auh mnu`K v`fy BwgW vwly hn, ijhVy gurU dI srn pYNdy hn,
sdw-iQr pRBU dy nwm ivc auhnW dI surq sdw juVI rihMdI hY[
