prmwqmw dw piv`qr nwm aus dy mn ivc Aw v`sdw hY[
ijhVy mnu`K sdw Awpxy gurU dI srn pey rihMdy hn, auhnW dy AMdroN haumY dUr ho jWdI hY ]12]
jdoN mnu`K gurU pwsoN (shI jIvn-rwh dw aupdyS) smJ lYNdw hY, qdoN aus nUM prmwqmw dw dr id`s pYNdw hY (Bwv, aus nUM ieh id`s pYNdw hY ik hir-nwm hI pRBU-imlwp dw vsIlw hY)[
pr ijhVw mnu`K nwm qoN s`Kxw hY auh (hornW nUM) viKAwn kr kr ky (Awp AMdroN iqRSnw dI A`g ivc) sVdw rihMdw hY[
gurU dI srn pYx dI brkiq ieh hY ik mnu`K (Awpxy AMdroN mwieAw dI) iqRSnw (mwieAw dI) Bu`K dUr kr lYNdw hY ]13]
pr, (jIvW dy kIh v`s?) prmwqmw Awp hI jIv nUM iml pey, qdoN hI auh (shI jIvn-rwh nUM) smJdw hY[
