(swrI Kyf prmwqmw dI rzw ivc ho rhI hY) Dur drgwh qoN (rzw Anuswr jIv dy m`Qy auqy jo lyK) iliKAw jWdw hY, auhI krm jIv kmWdw rihMdw hY[
